OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784081889
OL,3,CFans say time for 'Hand of God'
OL,4,Crevenge as England set for Argentina
OL,5,Csemi-final
OL,7,FEngland fans have said it is time for
OL,8,F"revenge for the Hand of God" as
OL,9,Fsupporters backed the Three Lions to
OL,10,Freach the World Cup final if they can
OL,11,Fstop Argentina captain Lionel Messi.
OL,13,FThousands of England supporters have
OL,14,Fdescended on Atlanta ahead of
OL,15,FWednesday's semi-final.
OL,17,FEngland manager Thomas Tuchel said his
OL,18,Fside were ready to face an Argentina
OL,19,Fteam "fuelled by history" as they bid
OL,20,Fto reach a first men's World Cup final
OL,21,Fsince 1966.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@]O]{D@FOU{D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784081889
OL,3,CFans say time for 'Hand of God'
OL,4,Crevenge as England set for Argentina
OL,5,Csemi-final
OL,7,FHe told reporters on Tuesday that much
OL,8,Fof the challenge would be preventing
OL,9,FMessi from producing another moment of
OL,10,Fbrilliance.
OL,12,FTuchel said his players had the "grit"
OL,13,Fand mentality to overcome the reigning
OL,14,Fchampions, despite describing the 39-
OL,15,Fyear-old as a unique talent who "sees
OL,16,Fstuff earlier than anyone else on the
OL,17,Ffield".
OL,26,@tD@aOUtD@fO]wD@aOUyD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784081889
OL,3,CFans say time for 'Hand of God'
OL,4,Crevenge as England set for Argentina
OL,5,Csemi-final
OL,7,FHe added that he considered using
OL,8,F"proper old school man-marking" to
OL,9,Fstop the Argentina captain, who has
OL,10,Fscored eight goals at what is expected
OL,11,Fto be his final World Cup.
OL,13,FPolice introduced a number of road
OL,14,Fblocks in the city centre on Tuesday
OL,15,Fnight after security was stepped up
OL,16,Facross Atlanta ahead of the game.
OL,18,FWhile confidence in Tuchel's side was
OL,19,Fhigh among England supporters in
OL,20,FAtlanta, most identified Messi as the
OL,21,Fkey threat.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784081889
OL,3,CFans say time for 'Hand of God'
OL,4,Crevenge as England set for Argentina
OL,5,Csemi-final
OL,7,FMark Lester, 56, from London, said
OL,8,FEngland's task was straightforward.
OL,10,FHe told the Press Association: "I
OL,11,Fthink we'll win tomorrow.
OL,13,F"Just stop Messi. I know they've got
OL,14,Fother people, but they haven't got
OL,15,Fother people really.
OL,17,F"They've got Premiership players, who
OL,18,Faren't as good as our Premiership
OL,19,Fplayers, and I'm very confident, very
OL,20,Fconfident."
OL,26,@rD@`OUuD@AOUyD@AOU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784081889
OL,3,CFans say time for 'Hand of God'
OL,4,Crevenge as England set for Argentina
OL,5,Csemi-final
OL,7,FHis son Colin Lester, 25, agreed that
OL,8,FEngland had the stronger team.
OL,10,FHe said: "Attacking-wise, we've had
OL,11,Flike the highest XG (expected goals)
OL,12,Fover the whole tournament and they're
OL,13,Fa bit weak at the back.
OL,15,F"I think player for player, we're
OL,16,Fbetter than Argentina. Stop Messi.
OL,18,F"We'll get goals against Argentina `
OL,19,Fit's just whether he produces a bit of
OL,20,Fmagic."
OL,26,@rD@JOUwD@AOUzD@AOU|D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784081889
OL,3,CFans say time for 'Hand of God'
OL,4,Crevenge as England set for Argentina
OL,5,Csemi-final
OL,7,FWhile watching Spain beat France 2-0
OL,8,Fin the other semi-final, England fans
OL,9,Fwere still discussing Diego Maradona's
OL,10,Fcontroversial "Hand of God" goal 40
OL,11,Fyears after it knocked the Three Lions
OL,12,Fout of the 1986 World Cup.
OL,14,FMark Lester said: "Maradona, they
OL,15,Fcelebrated that as if it was the
OL,16,Fbiggest game in the world because he
OL,17,Fcheated.
OL,19,F"I do not like them ` it is the
OL,20,Fbiggest game for us."
OL,26,@rD@OOUrD@[O]vD@SOU{D@AOU|D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784081889
OL,3,CFans say time for 'Hand of God'
OL,4,Crevenge as England set for Argentina
OL,5,Csemi-final
OL,7,FSimon Rowlinson, 61, from
OL,8,FWolverhampton, also wanted "revenge"
OL,9,Ffor the game in 1986.
OL,11,F"It's our time for getting revenge for
OL,12,Fthe Hand of God and everything else,"
OL,13,Fhe said.
OL,15,F"We're definitely going to win it, but
OL,16,Fit will be a tight game."
OL,26,@pD@\OUpD@dO]sD@AOUtD@eO]wD@AOUxD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784081889
OL,3,CFans say time for 'Hand of God'
OL,4,Crevenge as England set for Argentina
OL,5,Csemi-final
OL,7,FHis friend Mark Green, also 61 and
OL,8,Ffrom Wolverhampton, said beating
OL,9,FArgentina would carry a significance
OL,10,Fthat extended beyond a place in the
OL,11,Ffinal.
OL,13,F"It's got to be, hasn't it? It has
OL,14,Fabsolutely got to be ` just to get one
OL,15,Fover them," he said.
OL,17,F"Forget about all the politics and all
OL,18,Fof that because that's rubbish ` it's
OL,19,Fjust all about getting one over
OL,20,FArgentina on the football field."
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@KO]yD@AOU|D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784081889
OL,3,CFans say time for 'Hand of God'
OL,4,Crevenge as England set for Argentina
OL,5,Csemi-final
OL,7,FDespite their confidence, some
OL,8,Fsupporters expressed concern about
OL,9,Fofficiating.
OL,11,FMr Green said: "I think we'll always
OL,12,Fhave to play against the referee.
OL,14,F"So I think we know we're going to be
OL,15,Fup against it ` but you've got to do
OL,16,Fwhat you've got to do to win, haven't
OL,17,Fyou."
OL,19,FThe comments came after American
OL,20,Freferee Ismail Elfath was appointed to
OL,21,Ftake charge of the semi-final.
OL,26,@sD@POUvD@AOUyD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784081889
OL,3,CFans say time for 'Hand of God'
OL,4,Crevenge as England set for Argentina
OL,5,Csemi-final
OL,7,FMr Rowlinson, however, dismissed
OL,8,Fsuggestions England would be treated
OL,9,Funfairly.
OL,11,F"I'm not so bothered about the referee
OL,12,Fto be honest, because we've always got
OL,13,FVAR to back it up," he said.
OL,15,F"I'm not a big believer that referees
OL,16,Fhave been against certain teams ` I
OL,17,Fthink they're pretty fair."
OL,19,FElsewhere among England fans in
OL,20,FAtlanta, confidence remained the
OL,21,Fdominant mood.
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@SO]wD@AOUyD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784081889
OL,3,CFans say time for 'Hand of God'
OL,4,Crevenge as England set for Argentina
OL,5,Csemi-final
OL,7,FFreddie Bunn, 23, from Cheddar,
OL,8,FSomerset, said the match represented
OL,9,Fone of the biggest occasions of the
OL,10,Ftournament so far.
OL,12,F"I'm feeling very confident," he said.
OL,14,F"I think it's a big game for England,
OL,15,Fobviously, but not just a big game for
OL,16,FEngland, for Messi as well ` possibly
OL,17,Fhis last World Cup game.
OL,19,F"I think it's huge ` but feeling
OL,20,Fconfident."
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@]O]vD@AOU{D@AOU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784081889
OL,3,CFans say time for 'Hand of God'
OL,4,Crevenge as England set for Argentina
OL,5,Csemi-final
OL,7,FMr Bunn described Argentina as
OL,8,FEngland's biggest footballing rivals
OL,9,Fof the World Cup but said relations
OL,10,Fbetween the two sets of supporters had
OL,11,Fso far been positive.
OL,13,F"It's probably the biggest rivalry
OL,14,FEngland have faced so far in the
OL,15,Ftournament," he said.
OL,17,F"The Argentinians have been very
OL,18,Ffriendly towards us so hopefully there
OL,19,Fwon't be any trouble."
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@LO]yD@AOU{D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784081889
OL,3,CFans say time for 'Hand of God'
OL,4,Crevenge as England set for Argentina
OL,5,Csemi-final
OL,7,FAlex Kesley, 23, from Bristol, was
OL,8,Famong those predicting England would
OL,9,Fproduce their best performance of the
OL,10,Ftournament.
OL,12,F"So far in this tournament, we haven't
OL,13,Fproved how good we really are," he
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"I'll be honest, Jude Bellingham's got
OL,17,Fus through a few games, but this is
OL,18,Four time and I'm sure we're going to
OL,19,Fturn up tomorrow."
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@_O]xD@AOU{D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784081889
OL,3,CFans say time for 'Hand of God'
OL,4,Crevenge as England set for Argentina
OL,5,Csemi-final
OL,7,FHe continued: "And then, Tuchel knows
OL,8,Fhow to win finals ` he's got a proven
OL,9,Ftrack record."
OL,11,FAsked about the rivalry between the
OL,12,Ftwo nations, Mr Kesley said: "It's
OL,13,Fdefinitely up there.
OL,15,F"The atmosphere for the whole World
OL,16,FCup so far has been really sweet, and
OL,17,Fwe've had an amazing time.
OL,19,F"So hopefully it will stay nice and
OL,20,Fcalm."
OL,26,@oD@OOUqD@NO]tD@^OUwD@AOU{D@AOU|D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784081889
OL,3,CFans say time for 'Hand of God'
OL,4,Crevenge as England set for Argentina
OL,5,Csemi-final
OL,7,FBut despite describing relations
OL,8,Fbetween supporters as friendly, he
OL,9,Fwarned emotions could run high after
OL,10,Fthe final whistle.
OL,12,F"I can see it kicking off, no matter
OL,13,Fwho loses, to be honest," he said.
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@YO]
